and a bag of carob pretzels.

00:13.280 --> 00:14.907
That's all they had
in the mini-bar.

00:14.949 --> 00:18.316
Why don't you put that crap down
and come over here?

00:21.555 --> 00:24.991
Hello, girls.
Remember me?

00:25.025 --> 00:26.856
Dumpling? Have you had
some work done?

00:26.894 --> 00:28.953
I can barely get
my hands around them.

00:28.996 --> 00:30.964
They're exactly the same size.

00:30.998 --> 00:35.697
- Are you riding your menstrual cycle?
- No! What are you getting at?

00:35.736 --> 00:37.966
That maybe you're hiding
something from me?

00:38.005 --> 00:40.667
Like a little gift
that Phantom Limb left in your oven.

00:40.708 --> 00:42.903
All right.
I knew you couldn't handle this.

00:42.943 --> 00:45.810
It's crazy! We've been meeting
in this crappy hotel...

00:45.846 --> 00:48.644
like, three times a week
and it's going nowhere!

00:48.682 --> 00:52.118
All right, fine, I'll do Thursdays, too!
But only for, like, an hour.

00:52.152 --> 00:54.643
