to begin without me.

00:56.690 --> 01:00.023
Gee, thanks. Look, I keep coming
home with welts on my neck...

01:00.060 --> 01:02.654
and the
"I got jumped by Flying Squid" excuse...

01:02.696 --> 01:05.665
