a wee bit suspicious.

01:05.699 --> 01:07.963
Screw Phantom Limb!
No, wait, no, don't.

01:08.002 --> 01:10.334
Don't you get it?!
I love you!

01:10.371 --> 01:12.362
But I don't want this!

01:12.406 --> 01:14.499
All right. Fine!

01:14.541 --> 01:17.305
Oh, crap. You're crying. I... l...

01:17.344 --> 01:18.470
