down from all this!

01:21.482 --> 01:23.712
I should go.

01:23.751 --> 01:26.151
- Marry me.
- You're being serious?

01:26.186 --> 01:28.051
Deadly serious!

01:28.956 --> 01:30.514
- Yes.
- Good! Done.

01:30.557 --> 01:32.422
Now get your ass back in that bed!

01:32.459 --> 01:35.087
But we need to make
some ground rules.

01:35.129 --> 01:39.498
One. No more of this "I need my space,
you're crowding me" crap.

01:39.533 --> 01:41.763
Fine, whatever.
Where were you hiding that list?

01:41.802 --> 01:44.566
