I'm your partner.

01:44.605 --> 01:46.664
OK. I'll get you
a crown or something.

01:46.707 --> 01:50.199
Anything else on that magic
and probably moist list of yours?

01:50.244 --> 01:53.873
Yes, number three.
This whole Dr. Venture thing is over.

01:53.914 --> 01:56.178
Yes! We kill him once and for all!

01:56.216 --> 01:58.446
And we shall make
slaves of his sons...

01:58.485 --> 02:00.715
and a lamp from the flesh
of Brock Samson!

02:00.754 --> 02:02.415
No! I want you to give up...

02:02.456 --> 02:05.721
this insane grudge you have
with Dr. Venture once and for all!

02:05.759 --> 02:08.785
No way!
Dr. Venture is my sworn enemy!

02:08.829 --> 02:11.024
Never mind then,
I knew you weren't serious!

02:11.065 --> 02:12.123
No, no, don't go!

02:13.901 --> 02:17.632
Fine, I'll do it.
No more arching Dr. Venture.

02:17.671 --> 02:19.229
- Ever?
- Never.

02:19.273 --> 02:21.798
- Swear.
- I pinky swear!

02:22.710 --> 02:24.905
